Song: Maya Teri Ram
Rap & Lyrics: Narci
Singer: Late Shree Rajeshwaranand Ji Maharaj 
Music & Arrangement: Narci
Mixing & Mastering: XZEUS
Artwork/Poster & Lyrical Video: iKillGraphix

ABOUT 'MAYA TERI RAM' SONG
Attachment and illusion are created by God, the presence of attachment and illusion is natural but how it dominates you is what matters. Money is fine as long as it is in your pocket, but if this money dominates your mind then your downfall is certain. Money fulfills your needs, feeds your family. Hard-earned money and dreams fulfilled with money are never wrong, but if they are kept in your hands without any importance, then you will probably never be able to understand its value. The illusion of the world will always be in front of you but it depends on you whether you adopt this illusion in a positive or negative way.
